author: Kate McCann
title: Jeremy Corbyn refuses to confirm he will wear white tie to state dinner
text: Politics Jeremy Corbyn refuses to confirm he will wear white tie to state dinner The Labour leader will be 'appropriately attired', according to a spokesman, who refused to say whether he will be wearing white tie or lounge suit The Chinese flag will be flying in the UK this week for the state visit Photo: Alamy By Kate McCann , Senior Political Correspondent 3:21PM BST 19 Oct 2015
